<h1>Create a new set of objects</h1>

<form class="wy-form-stacked" {{action createType on="submit"}}>
  <div class="wh-content-type-create-form">
    <div class="wy-alert wy-alert-info">
      <div class="wy-alert-title">Just some advice on naming your set</div>
      Lowercase with no spaces only. <strong>Example:</strong> Comics, portfolio, people, trees, dragons, robots. It's usually common to use the plural form of a word, but not required.
    </div>
    <div class="wy-control-group fluid-input">
      <div class="wy-control">
        <div class="wy-inline-validate wy-inline-validate-warning">
          {{input value=newTypeName placeholder="ex: comics" class="wy-input-large"}}

          {{#if isDuplicate}}
            <span class="wy-input-context"> There is already an content type with that name</span>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {{#if newTypeName}}
      <div class="wy-button-group">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-neutral fa fa-check-circle"> Let's create a {{#if newTypeName}}{{newTypeName}}{{else}}comics{{/if}} form</button>
      </div>
    {{/if}}
    <p></p>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <h5>How the URLs will look for this set</h5>
  <ul class="wy-plain-list-disc">
    <li>A list of all <code>{{#if newTypeName}}{{newTypeName}}{{else}}comics{{/if}}</code> will exist at <code>http://www.yoursite.com/{{#if newTypeName}}{{newTypeName}}{{else}}comics{{/if}}</code></li>
    <li>Individual <code>{{#if newTypeName}}{{newTypeName}}{{else}}comics{{/if}}</code> will exist at <code>http://www.yoursite.com/{{#if newTypeName}}{{newTypeName}}{{else}}comics{{/if}}/$name/</code></li>
  </ul>

  <h5>Editable HTML templates will be generated in</h5>

  <ul class="wy-plain-list-disc">
    <li>The list template will exist in <code>/templates/{{#if newTypeName}}{{newTypeName}}{{else}}comics{{/if}}/list.swig</code></li>
    <li>The template for a single <code>{{#if newTypeName}}{{newTypeName}}{{else}}comics{{/if}}</code> will exist in <code>/templates/{{#if newTypeName}}{{newTypeName}}{{else}}comics{{/if}}/indivudal.swig</code></li>
  </ul>
</form>
